  Library preparation preflight produced setup context.
  
  Summary: The Kafka binder needs a reachable Kafka broker for meaningful producer/consumer binding coverage; upstream tests use Spring Kafka's embedded-broker test support.
  
  Already applied by Forge:
  - Add testImplementation dependency org.springframework.kafka:spring-kafka-test:4.0.2 (applied)
  
  Agent guidance:
